Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So this is Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:52.43,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(310,115)}The Fifty-Sixth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:52.43,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}The Answer to His Millennium
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya... Kouyou...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and... Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.60,Background,,0,0,0,,Your important match is next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.56,Background,,0,0,0,,I don't mind you coming here to relax, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.33,Background,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try to enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you enjoy being with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing I enjoy more than Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.03,Background,,0,0,0,,What a boring man you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose if you don't relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cheering you on, so don't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you even know what title I'm playing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:03.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I lost the Honinbou match against Master\NKuwabara in the last game, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll stop by the hospital on my way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and check up on my opponent\Nfor the Jyudan match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.36,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs11\1c&H4B2E9F&\shad1\bord0\frz7\fscy140\move(368,490,368,218)\frx12\fry345}AISHINDOU\NHOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.62,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs27.5\1c&H4A2D34&\bord0\pos(342,116)}N\NO\N\N\NV\NI\NS\NI\NT\NO\NR\NS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No visitors!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.25,Background,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to Master Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only up there because Touya-san\Nasked us to put it up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he doesn't want\Nanybody bothering him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:52.58,Background,,0,0,0,,He's really focused on playing Go on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet Go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.15,Background,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:05:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just went in to pick up the plates from his\Nlunch, but he hasn't touched any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all Go players like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Just who is he playing? Someone he\Nneeds to turn away visitors for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And he requested that he have no visitors ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:25.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then... this match was scheduled ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When did he schedule it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And with who!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.44,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs125\1c&H6C522B&\3c&HEEDEB6&\bord22\blur0\shad0\fscy150\pos(415,-43)}WHITE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!? They're already near the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't expanding from there let him win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something we're not seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's try playing it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.66,Memory,,0,0,0,,Mother, aren't you going to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:34.33,Memory,,0,0,0,,Your father told me not to come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.92,Memory,,0,0,0,,He told you not to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:41.30,Memory,,0,0,0,,He said he wants to play Go on the Internet\Nwithout getting interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:45.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He knew about this match before today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Father scheduled this ahead of time with Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya played a Nozoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nozoki!? From there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that seem too small to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, he's going to play there after\Nhe gains territory on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he wants to get Sente there\Nand then go to the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.09,Background,,0,0,0,,I think expanding there is fine though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.87,Background,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that result in a Miai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Touya-kun may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't Black win by just defending?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Black has the advantage,\Nit's incredibly small.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Meijin must have decided that he can't\Nbeat this opponent by just defending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably decided on solidly taking territory\Nwhile eliminating the white territory on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai can read incredibly deep\Nand calculate very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes up with a move to\Ntake control of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,after reading all of his opponent’s moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't let my father keep his\Nlead without putting up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai definitely won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I played him once during the\Nsummer two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai disappeared from the Internet\Nafter that match against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the same Sai is now playing\NGo on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And against Master Touya of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:37.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My father... arranged this match\Nagainst Sai ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Father knows who Sai is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:47.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But... the only time Father left the hospital was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,for the fourth game of the Jyudan match...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Did he arrange to play Sai then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then with someone who visited him at the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Could... one of them have been Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.21,Memory,,0,0,0,,Say, Akira-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.65,Memory,,0,0,0,,He's such a nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.20,Memory,,0,0,0,,He came to visit the Master at the hospital today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.87,Memory,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun came to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou came to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,can't forget about Shindou and Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:34.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If the Master were to have arranged this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He must have met him face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:42.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The Master doesn't know how to use e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then it must have been someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:48.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,who was around during the fourth\Ngame of the Jyudan match...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.78,Thinking,,0,0,0,,someone who came to see him at the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No. Shindou is not Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.62,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fs55\fad(417,0)\1c&H2F2E2C&\bord0\blur1\shad0\fscy50\move(355,213,210,213)}The 9th Annual Wakajishisen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,His game during the Wakajishisen was not\Na game that Sai would have played.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Besides, if he was Sai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,he would have become well-known\Neven when he was an Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:15.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But... even if Shindou isn't Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He might know who Sai is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But even if Shindou doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Someone around me is connected to Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.33,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even though he can play this\Nwell against Touya Kouyou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:36.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Just who is he!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any ideas, Touya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as to who Sai is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:00.97,Memory,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.93,Memory,,0,0,0,,Are you Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,have any ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he's playing this well against Master Touya,\Nthe number one Go player, with five titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to be a well-known pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be a pro from China or Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you find out where he's\Naccessing the net from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to trace him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if I knew more about the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai is not Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai is as strong as the most experienced\Nplayers imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:56.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I remember... the match we played\Non the Internet, two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My opponent, shrouded in darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yes! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You can't be Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:06.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If you're not Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why do I see the old Shindou in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:23.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The old Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:25.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Back when we first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Black is leading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:50.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ooyose is about to end as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't feel any doubt coming out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,From this opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I feel spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.33,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can feel it because I'm playing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:08.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've felt it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've felt it all before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This is!
