Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.81,Background,,0,0,0,,A good move...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.74,Background,,0,0,0,,He can't capture this white stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.70,Background,,0,0,0,,The black territory there... just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was close to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But now... Black's lost out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battle of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's played against you, you realize that it's\Nthe best move you can make in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But... how many people are\Nable to notice this move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people can make this move!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya's moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,None of them looks like a bad move, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.19,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2E260E&\fs20\blur1\bord0\shad0\fscx100\fscy110\pos(585,33)}Captured:
